item.title: Stainless-steel-series-distribution-box
item.description: The stainless steel series distribution box is a kind of distribution box designed and assembled into various control functions according to the model and specification of the components. Since the size of the box body can be selected arbitrarily, the structure is compact to a quite perfect combination. Wall-mounted installation, it can be used as a see-through window and door, and the door panel is pasted with a sealing rubber strip to prevent rainwater from infiltrating.
